## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the subjective nature of opinion-based sources. Additionally, the complexity of homelessness as a social issue means that solutions may vary significantly based on local contexts and resources. Further research could benefit from more empirical studies and data-driven analyses to complement the predominantly opinion-based sources used in this report.

